## Compare the four

### Vector

* ordered
* growable
* usually same-type values

### Tuple

* ordered
* fixed length
* can mix types

### Struct

* named fields
* best for one clearly structured record

### HashSet / HashMap

* `HashSet` for unique values
* `HashMap` for key-value storage

